# Figma Color Mapping

When implementing designs from Figma MCP, use these lookup tables to translate Figma semantic color names to CSS variables.

**CRITICAL RULES:**
- When Figma MCP references ANY color, look up the exact CSS variable from these tables
- NEVER use hex values directly in components
- NEVER use foundational tokens (like `--neutral-base-700`) directly - use semantic variables
- NEVER guess - if a color isn't in these tables, ask for clarification

