## Usage Examples

### Background fill from Figma
```tsx
// Figma shows: Background/Secondary
<div style={{ backgroundColor: 'var(--ds-bg-secondary)' }}>
```

### Text color from Figma
```tsx
// Figma shows: Text/Secondary
<span style={{ color: 'var(--ds-text-secondary)' }}>Label</span>
```

### Border from Figma
```tsx
// Figma shows: Border/Input
<input style={{ borderColor: 'var(--color-border-input)' }} />
```

### Icon color from Figma
```tsx
// Figma shows: Icon/Primary
<Icon style={{ color: 'var(--ds-icon-primary)' }} />
```
